    "title": "Replacing Foundation Timers with Timer Publishers"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If your app uses Foundation’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " class",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to repeatedly receive a callback or invoke a closure on a specified interval, you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "can convert these instances to Combine to simplify your code.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Performing-Periodic-Work-with-a-Timer",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Performing Periodic Work with a Timer",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Consider the following snippet, which uses ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/2091889-scheduledtimer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to update the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "lastUpdated",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " property of a data model once a second, on a specific",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "dispatch queue:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "var timer: Timer?",
            "override func viewDidLoad() {",
            "    super.viewDidLoad()",
            "    timer = Timer.scheduledTimer(withTimeInterval: 1, repeats: true) { _ in",
            "        self.myDispatchQueue.async() {",
            "            self.myDataModel.lastUpdated = Date()",
            "        }",
            "    }",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Converting-to-a-Timer-Publisher",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Converting to a Timer Publisher",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To migrate this code to Combine, replace the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that is returned by ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/2091889-scheduledtimer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "with a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/timerpublisher",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". You create",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "this publisher with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/3329589-publish",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Every time the underyling ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " fires,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the publisher emits a new ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/date",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " that represents",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the instant the timer fired. You then apply Combine operators to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/date",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ",",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "eventually connecting the publisher to a subscriber like ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/Publisher/sink(receiveValue:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/Publisher/assign(to:on:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Because ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/timerpublisher",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " conforms to the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/ConnectablePublisher",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " protocol, it won’t produce elements until you explicitly connect to it. Do this by either calling ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/ConnectablePublisher/connect()",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", or using an ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/ConnectablePublisher/autoconnect()",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " operator to connect automatically when a subscriber attaches.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Tip",
          "style": "tip",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The next example shows how to use a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/timerpublisher",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to replace the previous example. It uses Combine’s operators to perform the tasks",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that were in the previous example’s closure:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "var cancellable: Cancellable?",
            "override func viewDidLoad() {",
            "    super.viewDidLoad()",
            "    cancellable = Timer.publish(every: 1, on: .main, in: .default)",
            "        .autoconnect()",
            "        .receive(on: myDispatchQueue)",
            "        .assign(to: \\.lastUpdated, on: myDataModel)",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In this example, Combine operators replace all the behavior inside the closure of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the earlier example:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/Publisher/receive(on:options:)",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " operator ensures",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "that its subsequent operators run on the specified dispatch queue. This replaces",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "async()",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " call from before.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Combine/documentation/Combine/Publisher/assign(to:on:)",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " operator updates the data",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "model, by using a key path to set the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "lastUpdate",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " property.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Another advantage you’ll find when using Combine to simplify your code is that the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer/timerpublisher",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " produces new ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/date",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "instances as its output type. The first example’s closure receives the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/timer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "itself as its parameter, so it has to create new ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/date",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "instances manually.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
